  "name": "Linkly Troubleshooting > Passwords / Printer options",
  "body": "<h1 data-id=\"linkly-troubleshooting-passwords-printer-options\">Linkly Troubleshooting &gt; Passwords / Printer options</h1>\n<p>This guide is for the use of Troubleshooting Linkly</p>\n<p>Including:</p>\n<ol><li><span><strong>Getting the banks username and password (including merchant and terminal ID)</strong></span></li><li><span><strong>Changing the Auto Print Receipt checkbox and Cut Receipt checkbox</strong></span></li><li><span><strong>If the Linkly GUI interface (Green C) not printing Settlements/Logons</strong></span></li></ol><p><span><strong>!</strong><strong> ATTENTION !</strong></span><span><strong> IT IS VERY IMPORTANT TO DELETE THESE BATCH SCRIPTS FROM THE CLIENTS COMPUTER, THESE SCRIPTS CAN BE EDITED AND COULD CAUSE DAMAGE IF A UNWANTED USER EDITS OR ADJUSTS VALUES WITHIN THE SCRIPT (</strong></span><span><strong>SHIFT + DELETE</strong></span><span><strong> &gt; DELETE PERMANENTLY)</strong></span></p>\n<div><span>! <span>UPDATE</span> ! These SCRIPTS now DELETE THEMSELVES!!</span></div><br/><br/><div>\n<p><span><span>If the batch scripts get stuck at any point in time &gt; EG: Linkly client is stopping.....</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>And will not continue, click inside the console and press '<strong>any key</strong>', this should continue the script.</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>All Scripts close automatically</span></span></p>\n</div>\n<p><span>These Scripts restart the Linkly Service, please wait for Linkly to turn green after running through the <strong>Adjust Linkly Printer.bat </strong>and <strong>Linkly add GUI print.bat</strong></span></p>\n<p><img alt=\"rtaImage - 2023-07-08T180328.159.png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTEIEA2.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTEIEA2.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTEIEA2.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTEIEA2.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTEIEA2.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTEIEA2.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTEIEA2.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTEIEA2.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<p> </p>\n<hr></hr><br/><div><span><strong>Due to a new Update of Linkly software --<br/>The Username and Password script may not work -- due to Linkly now encrypting the password within the registry</strong></span></div>\n<h3 data-id=\"get-the-username-and-password-for-bank-from-linkly\"><strong>Get the Username and Password for Bank from Linkly</strong></h3>\n<ol><li>This will show the credentials of\n<ol><li><strong>IDENT &gt; USERNAME</strong></li><li><strong>PASSWORD</strong></li><li><strong>MERCHANT ID </strong>(if needed &gt; mainly for bank / Fiserv)</li><li><strong>TERMINAL ID</strong> (if needed &gt; mainly for bank / Fiserv)</li></ol></li><li>Check the Server GUI from the Linkly Software if it contains a Username and Password in the server tab<br/><img alt=\"rtaImage - 2023-07-08T180334.277.png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppT52EAE.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppT52EAE.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppT52EAE.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppT52EAE.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppT52EAE.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppT52EAE.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppT52EAE.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppT52EAE.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img><br/><img alt=\"rtaImage - 2023-07-08T180340.831.png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTESEA2.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTESEA2.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTESEA2.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTESEA2.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTESEA2.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTESEA2.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTESEA2.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTESEA2.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></li><li>If the Ident field contains 'EFTSRV1'\n<ol><li>the Server is using the Internal Pinpad's 3g/4g network and won't need the password, even if the password field has a password inside (most likely empty).</li><li>You won't need the script for this if the field is 'EFTSRV1'<br/><img alt=\"rtaImage - 2023-07-08T180350.024.png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTEmEAM.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTEmEAM.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTEmEAM.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTEmEAM.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTEmEAM.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTEmEAM.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTEmEAM.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTEmEAM.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></li></ol></li><li>Run the script provided called '<strong>Get EFT pass.bat</strong>'</li><li>Reference the Picture below to understand what value belong to which Registry request\n<ol><li>Ident REG_SZ = <strong>IDENT (USERNAME)</strong></li><li>PWORD REG_SZ = <strong>PASSWORD</strong></li><li>MERCHANTID REG_SZ = <strong>MERCHANT ID</strong></li><li>TERMINALID REG_SZ = <strong>TERMINAL ID</strong><br/><img alt=\"rtaImage - 2023-07-08T180419.180.png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTEwEAM.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTEwEAM.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTEwEAM.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTEwEAM.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTEwEAM.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTEwEAM.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTEwEAM.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTEwEAM.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></li></ol></li><li>The Batch Script will close automatically</li><li><span>! IMPORTANT !</span> Delete file after</li></ol><hr></hr><h3 data-id=\"change-auto-print-always-cut-and-printer-selection-feature-without-running-through-the-linkly-setup-config\"><strong>Change Auto Print, Always Cut and Printer selection feature (without running through the Linkly setup config)</strong></h3>\n<div><br/><div><span>When you First execute the script, it will display the current values of the</span></div>\n<p><strong>- Current Printer Name</strong></p>\n<p><strong>- Auto Print receipt option</strong></p>\n<p><strong>- Cut Receipt option</strong></p>\n</div>\n<p>0x1 = value of 1 which == <strong>CHECKED</strong> in Checkbox</p>\n<hr></hr><p>0x0 = value of 0 which == <strong>UN-CHECKED</strong> in Checkbox</p>\n<p><img alt=\"rtaImage - 2023-07-08T180437.241.png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTF1EAM.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTF1EAM.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTF1EAM.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTF1EAM.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTF1EAM.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTF1EAM.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTF1EAM.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTF1EAM.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<hr></hr><ol><li>Drop the <strong>Adjust Linkly Printer.bat </strong>script into the PC<br/>\t </li><li>Open script it will first ask '<strong>Do you want to change the Printer NPT is the internal EFTPOS printer (Y/N)?</strong>' this will change the name of the printer, pressing '<strong>y</strong>' will say yes to change printer name -- pressing '<strong>n</strong>' will continue to the next step and keep the same printer name<br/><br/><img alt=\"rtaImage - 2023-07-08T180449.678.png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppSXVEA2.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppSXVEA2.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppSXVEA2.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppSXVEA2.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppSXVEA2.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppSXVEA2.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppSXVEA2.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppSXVEA2.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></li><li>If you want to change the printer name, copy the exact name of the printer and type exactly into the batch script<br/>\t </li><li>The next stage will ask '<strong>Do you want to make changes to the Linkly Printer Override POS options? Y/N</strong>' this will continue to the checkboxes of the Auto print and the Auto cut feature during the Linkly wizard config<br/><br/><img alt=\"rtaImage - 2023-07-08T180455.182.png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTFLEA2.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTFLEA2.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTFLEA2.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTFLEA2.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTFLEA2.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTFLEA2.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTFLEA2.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTFLEA2.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></li><li>The next stage will ask '<strong>Enable Override POS AutoPrint (Linkly always prints)? Y(0x1)/N(0x0)</strong>' this will change the checkbox of the Auto print feature during the Linkly wizard config\n<ol><li>If you want the <strong>Checkbox </strong>&gt; <span>checked </span>&gt; Press '<strong>y</strong>'</li><li>If you want the <strong>Checkbox </strong>&gt; <span>unchecked</span> &gt; Press '<strong>n</strong>'<br/>\t\t </li></ol></li><li>The next stage will ask '<strong>Do you want to change Cut Receipt</strong>' this will change the checkbox of the Auto print feature during the Linkly wizard config\n<ol><li>If you want the <strong>Checkbox </strong>&gt; <span>checked</span> &gt; Press '<strong>y</strong>'</li><li>If you want the <strong>Checkbox </strong>&gt; <span>unchecked</span> &gt; Press '<strong>n</strong>'</li></ol></li><li>Reference picture below for the Y/N selection<br/><br/><img alt=\"rtaImage - 2023-07-08T180500.743.png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTFpEAM.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTFpEAM.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTFpEAM.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTFpEAM.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTFpEAM.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTFpEAM.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTFpEAM.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppTFpEAM.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></li><li>Once the script is done, it will restart the Linkly client so the <strong>Green C </strong>will disappear and reappear Yellow &gt; Wait until it turns Green again.</li><li>The Batch Script will close automatically</li><li><span>! IMPORTANT !</span> This Script will prompt you for deletion</li></ol><hr></hr><h3 data-id=\"if-the-linkly-gui-green-c-doesn-t-print-from-the-gui-settlement-logon\"><strong>If the Linkly GUI (Green C) doesn't print from the GUI &gt; Settlement / Logon</strong></h3>\n<ol><li>Run the '<strong>Linkly add GUI print.bat</strong>', this will adjust the values</li><li>Once the script is done, it will restart the Linkly client so the <strong>Green C </strong>will disappear and reappear Yellow &gt; Wait until it turns Green again.</li><li>Test to ensure the script works</li><li>The Batch Script will close automatically</li><li><span>! IMPORTANT !</span> Delete file after</li></ol>",
